## Data Sources and Third-Party Licenses

This application uses channel data from the TVGarden/tv-garden-channel-list project
(https://github.com/TVGarden/tv-garden-channel-list), which is provided under an
unlicense/public domain license. The source and metadata streams (API data) are
from free/open sources and remain under their original licenses or as public domain/unlicense.

The r1-tv application is MIT-licensed as stated above. Channel data is NOT part of
the app itself and is loaded in real-time from third parties via open source/unlicense APIs.
Users and redistributors should verify the current license status of any data sources.
